{
  "title": "Test Dialogue",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "node:1",
      "type": "START",
      "position": "(700.0, 800.0)"
    },
    {
      "id": "node:2",
      "type": "DIALOGUE",
      "position": "(1180.0, 860.0)",
      "character": "uid://dks7iglsfui0y::3",
      "text": "Greetings, acting employee 14 or your preferred identity. We hope you’re familiar with the Bataafse orientation handbook, but we’ve found that a single friendly voice is often worth a thousand words on a pad. You can call me Mark3, your handler for this mission. I’m here to make sure your work experience is both pleasant and productive — think of those terms as two wings of the company motto, keeping us all in the air."
    },
    {
      "id": "node:3",
      "type": "DIALOGUE_OPTION",
      "position": "(1720.0, 640.0)",
      "character": "uid://dks7iglsfui0y::2",
      "text": "Cute."
    },
    {
      "id": "node:4",
      "type": "DIALOGUE_OPTION",
      "position": "(1720.0, 940.0)",
      "character": "uid://dks7iglsfui0y::2",
      "text": "So what am I doing here?"
    },
    {
      "id": "node:5",
      "type": "DIALOGUE_OPTION",
      "position": "(1720.0, 1300.0)",
      "character": "uid://dks7iglsfui0y::2",
      "text": "I forgot my briefing."
    },
    {
      "id": "node:6",
      "type": "DIALOGUE",
      "position": "(2300.0, 420.0)",
      "character": "uid://dks7iglsfui0y::3",
      "text": "I’m glad you think so. To get started, go to the central strut and locate the communications center. You should be able to get the door open with minimal issues. "
    },
    {
      "id": "node:7",
      "type": "DIALOGUE",
      "position": "(2327.0, 927.0)",
      "character": "uid://dks7iglsfui0y::3",
      "text": "Your mission is to assess the situation at Drenthe station and handle any issues. There’s no serious cause for concern, but we have detected some unexpected radio silence and power issues that we need to understand better. Make sure the station continues to operate, restart any systems, and in the unlikely scenario of a level 3 event, find all non-injured personnel. To get started, go to the central strut and locate the communications center. You should be able to get the door open with minimal issues. "
    }
  ],
